cs.DC, cs.DS, cs.SY, cs.PF, cs.LG. 

This paper deals with job scheduling in a MapReduce cluster, which is a distributed computing system. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.DC (Distributed, Parallel, and Cluster Computing). The paper also involves algorithms and performance analysis, which could fall under cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms) and cs.LG (Machine Learning). The use of weighted sum and competitive performance bounds suggests the possibility of cs.SY (Systems and Control) and cs.PF (Performance).
